<br>
Most people don't buff properly, that's why Naggy can kill a force of 40+. In fact, last weekend he took down 47 twice, and 40-something the next day, then we took over. We broke in. Cleared to safe hall. In safe hall, we buffed like this. 4 junks... 54 druid provided, but any druid can, designate one. 52 shammy. str/agi/sta/tali. 48 cleric symbol for melee. 41 cleric symbol for caster. 52 chanter GMR/haste/crack. 51 druid SLN and CoW.<br>
<br>
MA goes in, if summoned. let him die/rez/rebuff/try again. If not, let him get aggro. BTW, he attacks when celestial heal is proccing. Pally's LoH next. Melee attack. After LoH's burned clerics rotate CH best they can (They will be feared). Druids backup with SH/GH. Nukers go in at 50%. We got a 52 mage malo off at same time nuke call was made. Not sure how much difference that made, but Naggy went down fast. Lost about half our people. SA was still standing as were nukers.<br>
<br>
This is the plan for Naggy. Never done Vox. Somewhere a stun plan would have to be added. Hope this helps. If you're going in and see me on, send a tell, I'll come and bring what support I can.<br>
